1
00:00:39,719 --> 00:00:40,359
Who is it?

2
00:00:45,240 --> 00:00:46,479
It's Young Hero Yan.

3
00:00:47,159 --> 00:00:48,719
I want you to take me to find a certain medicine.

4
00:00:48,960 --> 00:00:49,799
What medicine?

5
00:00:50,840 --> 00:00:52,560
The medicine Yun Yang gave me.

6
00:00:54,719 --> 00:00:56,960
Young Hero Yan, you must be joking.

7
00:00:57,039 --> 00:00:58,000
This medicine...

8
00:00:58,079 --> 00:01:01,320
is the very foundation of our Peach Blossom Manor.

9
00:01:01,640 --> 00:01:03,159
How could the young master

10
00:01:03,159 --> 00:01:05,400
tell a mere servant like me?

11
00:01:06,400 --> 00:01:07,599
If you don't know,

12
00:01:07,959 --> 00:01:09,400
then you're of no use to me.

13
00:01:10,079 --> 00:01:10,599
I'm useful!

14
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:12,519
I'm useful!

15
00:01:21,719 --> 00:01:22,480
Young Hero Yan,

16
00:01:23,040 --> 00:01:27,200
all the medicines of Peach Blossom Manor are here.

17
00:01:27,959 --> 00:01:29,519
Where is the mind-altering medicine?

18
00:01:30,799 --> 00:01:31,599
Young Hero,

19
00:01:32,319 --> 00:01:34,159
