22
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:39,799
I'll cooperate!

23
00:01:40,439 --> 00:01:41,439
I'll definitely cooperate!

24
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:04,280
Young Hero Yan, look,

25
00:02:06,719 --> 00:02:09,360
this is our Peach Blossom Manor's

26
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:11,039
unique secret recipe.

27
00:02:11,319 --> 00:02:12,400
When using it,

28
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:15,479
you must pay attention to the dosage.

29
00:02:15,759 --> 00:02:17,639
Otherwise, it could be dangerous.

30
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:21,080
Look at its color.

31
00:02:54,199 --> 00:02:55,120
I haven't arrived yet.

32
00:02:56,479 --> 00:02:57,800
You want to use torture too?

33
00:02:58,479 --> 00:03:00,120
You’re really bold.

34
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:02,120
Young Master.

35
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:04,400
Are you feeling guilty?

36
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:06,879
Lord Han Dao, please don’t make baseless accusations.

37
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:09,840
The suspect Yan Shiyi took Uncle He hostage.

38
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,639
He tried to sneak into the pharmacy.

39
00:03:11,639 --> 00:03:12,879
To plant Peach Blossom Powder.

40
00:03:12,879 --> 00:03:14,400
To frame me.

41
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:16,199
I caught him in the act.

42
00:03:18,039 --> 00:03:19,560
I invited you here, my lord.

43
00:03:20,039 --> 00:03:22,919
Of course, I wanted to interrogate him with you.

44
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:23,960
Alright.

45
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:25,199
Please.

46
00:03:26,199 --> 00:03:26,879
Suspect.

47
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:28,680
Yan Shiyi.

48
00:03:30,479 --> 00:03:31,199
Let me ask you.

49
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:34,439
Why did the Young Master give you medicine?

50
00:03:35,919 --> 00:03:38,719
Yun Yang found out about my old friendship with Master Yun.

51
00:03:39,599 --> 00:03:40,879
He wanted to buy me off.

52
00:03:42,599 --> 00:03:45,120
What is the Young Master trying to do?

53
00:03:46,439 --> 00:03:47,719
This is a life-saving medicine.

54
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:53,080
But I, Yan, cannot accept a reward without merit.

55
00:03:54,759 --> 00:03:56,680
My father doesn’t need a servant like you.

56
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:58,840
But I am a good master.

57
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:05,479
