58
00:04:06,479 --> 00:04:07,680
I can save your life.

59
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:14,800
How do I know

60
00:04:15,520 --> 00:04:16,360
that in this medicine

61
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:18,040
you haven't poisoned me?

62
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:20,879
You're a disciple of the Qingshan Sect.

63
00:04:21,399 --> 00:04:23,240
The Qingshan Sect is famous for its medicine.

64
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:25,079
Whether it's the right remedy for the illness,

65
00:04:25,439 --> 00:04:26,560
you'll know once you try it.

66
00:04:30,639 --> 00:04:31,480
What do you want me to do?

67
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:33,959
I haven't decided yet.

68
00:04:34,959 --> 00:04:36,279
You haven't decided yet?

69
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:39,040
You're quite talented.

70
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:40,759
You're useful to my father,

71
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:42,680
and even more useful to me.

72
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:45,920
When I decide, you'll know.

73
00:04:46,759 --> 00:04:48,680
This medicine can ease your pain.

74
00:04:49,279 --> 00:04:50,639
As long as you belong to me,

75
00:04:51,399 --> 00:04:53,000
you'll never lack medicine from me.

76
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:57,319
Young Master,

77
00:04:58,199 --> 00:04:58,879
let me ask you,

78
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:01,959
what medicine did you give Yan Shiyi?

79
00:05:03,519 --> 00:05:06,199
Of course, it's the Longevity Powder.

80
00:05:06,199 --> 00:05:07,040
You're lying!

81
00:05:07,839 --> 00:05:10,399
The medicine you gave me clearly causes hallucinations.

82
00:05:11,519 --> 00:05:12,439
Nonsense.

83
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:15,519
This is a famous medicine from my Peach Blossom Manor.

84
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:17,319
You can ask around.

85
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:19,319
Many people have taken this medicine,

86
00:05:19,879 --> 00:05:22,560
but no one has ever reported hallucinations.

87
00:05:22,759 --> 00:05:23,680
That's nonsense!

88
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:24,439
You—

89
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:28,120
So you really do want to slander me.

90
00:05:28,879 --> 00:05:29,560
Guards!

91
00:05:29,839 --> 00:05:30,519
Search him!

92
00:05:30,839 --> 00:05:31,399
Wait!

93
00:05:35,199 --> 00:05:36,000
I'll do it.

94
00:05:38,079 --> 00:05:38,680
Please.

95
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,319
Junior disciple

96
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:50,879
You’ve recovered from your fever.

97
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:52,639
Aren’t you still alive too?

98
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:55,120
I’m just lucky.

99
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:56,959
I kept this worthless life

100
