00:06:49,839 --> 00:06:50,519
Cold Blade

107
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:51,399
Sir

108
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:52,720
Sir

109
00:06:56,639 --> 00:06:57,160
Sir

110
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:02,920
Yun Su

111
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:09,879
Sir, junior disciple

112
00:07:09,959 --> 00:07:10,600
Sir

113
00:07:19,759 --> 00:07:20,399
Sir

114
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:23,079
Are you alright?

115
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:30,480
So this is the hallucinogenic Peach Blossom Powder.

116
00:07:30,839 --> 00:07:33,399
The poison Yan Shiyi always carries.

117
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:35,079
You’re framing me.

118
00:07:37,639 --> 00:07:39,839
