120
00:07:46,279 --> 00:07:49,000
It seems that unless we use torture,

121
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:51,199
you won’t tell the truth.

122
00:07:53,040 --> 00:07:53,800
Yun Lang

123
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:56,639
Why did you lie to me?

124
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,759
If we can’t share a bed in life,

125
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:01,279
then let’s share a grave in death.

126
00:08:01,759 --> 00:08:02,399
Master

127
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:12,199
You—

128
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:23,279
