144
00:09:32,519 --> 00:09:33,399
Nonsense!

145
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:47,000
You—

146
00:09:50,039 --> 00:09:50,919
Junior brother,

147
00:09:51,679 --> 00:09:53,039
If you still don't believe me,

148
00:09:54,279 --> 00:09:55,600
go ahead and torture me.

149
00:09:56,639 --> 00:09:57,639
I'm fine.

150
00:10:01,759 --> 00:10:03,960
Sir, don't fall for his ruse.

151
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:07,799
I'm best at tormenting villains.

152
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:11,919
Applying salt water to a wound that's just about to heal—

153
00:10:11,919 --> 00:10:12,600
Enough.

154
00:10:14,159 --> 00:10:16,120
The suspect Yan Shiyi has been ill for a long time.

155
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:18,399
If the young master ends up killing him,

156
00:10:18,960 --> 00:10:21,399
