158
00:10:24,879 --> 00:10:25,879
There are two days left.

159
00:10:26,279 --> 00:10:27,159
Within these two days,

160
00:10:27,279 --> 00:10:28,600
I will definitely find the real culprit.

161
00:10:30,279 --> 00:10:31,159
During these two days,

162
00:10:31,799 --> 00:10:33,840
if anyone dares to torture Yan Shiyi—

163
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:40,039
Just like this chain,

164
00:10:43,159 --> 00:10:43,919
Young Master,

165
00:10:44,519 --> 00:10:45,639
now your cell

166
00:10:45,639 --> 00:10:47,159
has been requisitioned by the court for investigation.

167
00:10:48,039 --> 00:10:49,000
You have no objections, do you?

168
00:10:51,879 --> 00:10:52,960
If it's for the investigation,

169
00:10:52,960 --> 00:10:54,080
I naturally have no objections.

170
00:10:54,759 --> 00:10:57,840
But if it's for you and your fellow disciples to cover for each other,

171
00:10:58,799 --> 00:11:00,480
then I can only report it to the capital.

172
00:11:00,919 --> 00:11:02,039
And have you punished.

173
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:02,960
Of course.

174
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:04,799
Within two days,

175
00:11:05,399 --> 00:11:06,679
if I can't find the murderer,

176
00:11:07,759 --> 00:11:08,799
I will accept punishment myself.

177
00:11:08,799 --> 00:11:09,279
Alright.

178
00:11:09,919 --> 00:11:11,000
Then let's wait and see.

179
00:11:19,879 --> 00:11:20,519
Shiyi,

180
00:11:29,080 --> 00:11:29,919
you all may leave for now.

181
00:11:31,159 --> 00:11:31,919
Yes.

182
00:11:33,519 --> 00:11:34,159
Shiyi,

183
00:11:35,120 --> 00:11:35,840
Shiyi,

184
00:11:38,799 --> 00:11:39,480
Senior Brother,

185
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:41,799
I was wrong.

186
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:44,039
I wrongly blamed you.

187
00:11:45,960 --> 00:11:46,759
Yunyang,

188
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:49,039
go investigate Yunyang.

189
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:50,799
But

190
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:52,679
your purpose in coming to Peach Blossom Manor

191
00:11:52,679 --> 00:11:54,039
was to investigate Yun Su.

192
00:11:54,799 --> 00:11:56,360
Yun Su is already dead.

193
00:11:56,759 --> 00:11:58,080
Your mission is over.

194
00:11:58,519 --> 00:12:00,639
Why are you still holding onto Yunyang?

195
00:12:01,360 --> 00:12:02,679
That's not your concern.

196
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:04,039
Can't you

197
00:12:04,039 --> 00:12:05,960
think about your own life for once?

198
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:08,679
I...

199
00:12:10,919 --> 00:12:13,679
am your last family in this world.

200
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:16,159
I have to help you.

201
00:12:22,960 --> 00:12:23,799
Shiyi...

202
00:12:29,279 --> 00:12:29,879
Senior Brother

203
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:32,200
Senior Brother

204
00:12:58,279 --> 00:13:00,799
After all, how many people truly get what they seek?

205
00:13:01,519 --> 00:13:04,919
Who knows if we spend our days dreaming of being a fish?

206
00:13:05,639 --> 00:13:06,639
What are you trying to say?

207
00:13:07,360 --> 00:13:08,039
People, after all,

208
00:13:08,799 --> 00:13:11,519
