209
00:13:12,159 --> 00:13:14,440
The Master has already gotten what he wished for.

210
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:16,080
There's no need to blame yourself.

211
00:13:18,360 --> 00:13:19,559
Xiao Ying is dead.

212
00:13:20,559 --> 00:13:21,720
