234
00:16:01,559 --> 00:16:02,360
Father

235
00:16:02,879 --> 00:16:04,840
You are the son I am most proud of

236
00:16:05,480 --> 00:16:07,720
This position will be yours sooner or later

237
00:16:08,360 --> 00:16:09,279
Why are you in such a hurry?

238
00:16:10,120 --> 00:16:10,759
Impossible

239
00:16:12,360 --> 00:16:13,639
You are already dead

240
00:16:14,840 --> 00:16:16,000
I saw it with my own eyes

241
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:17,120
You can't fool me

242
00:16:26,759 --> 00:16:27,440
Brother

243
00:16:33,320 --> 00:16:33,919
Brother

244
00:16:34,720 --> 00:16:35,919
Did he change your blood again?

245
00:16:37,919 --> 00:16:39,639
Brother, you don't recognize me anymore

246
00:16:42,120 --> 00:16:43,039
It's me, Xiaoying

247
00:16:45,000 --> 00:16:45,799
Xiaoying

248
00:16:47,480 --> 00:16:48,360
