270
00:17:42,519 --> 00:17:43,200
Xiaoying

271
00:17:45,400 --> 00:17:46,319
Wake up.

272
00:17:49,000 --> 00:17:50,160
It's all fake.

273
00:17:51,839 --> 00:17:53,319
