277
00:18:20,799 --> 00:18:22,440
Look again and I'll gouge out your eyes.

278
00:18:24,240 --> 00:18:26,440
Say another word and I'll cut out your tongue.

279
00:18:30,839 --> 00:18:31,759
Who are you?

280
00:18:32,759 --> 00:18:34,240
